00:05:50.379 --> 00:05:53.699
Now, why is this so important that we fight this imperfect

00:05:53.699 --> 00:05:56.420
tendency that we all have toward pride,

00:05:56.420 --> 00:06:01.259
toward lacking humility, fearlings of superiority?

00:06:01.259 --> 00:06:03.860
Well, not only is it distasteful to Jehovah,

00:06:03.860 --> 00:06:07.180
